    <section id="id1169311449665">
      <title>Who am I?</title>
      <list id="id1169313512411" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Have a group discussion on the good qualities you would like to see in people.</item>
        <item>Also discuss the things that you don't like.</item>
        <item>Read the following words.</item>
        <item>Which of these words make you feel very bad? </item>
        <item>Colour the "bad" blocks green, and the "good" blocks red.</item>
      </list>
      <figure id="id1169313651145">
        <media id="id1169313651145_media" alt="">
          <image mime-type="image/jpg" src="../../media/graphics2-cc97.jpg" id="id1169313651145__onlineimage" height="197" width="630"/>
        </media>
      </figure>
      <list id="id1169321535027" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Write down another three good characteristics you discussed in your groups.</item>
        <item>Draw a picture in three blocks of the characteristics you like best.</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id1169311218864"/>
    </section>
    <section id="id1169319237394">
      <title>Mom and Dad each has an ID document.</title>
      <para id="id1169315755856">It states their date of birth and other information about themselves. The document also contains a small photograph.</para>
      <list id="id1169325804206" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Design your own ID document. Your document is going to be very special, because you must also write down your own good characteristics and talents.</item>
      </list>
